5|$|The {{film was}} {{released}} by Toei Company on 11 March 1984. The film would gross about 1.48 billion yen at the box office, sell 914,767 tickets and make an additional 742 million yen in distribution income. Home releases include the original April 1984 Laserdisc release {{and as part of}} Juburi ga Ippai Sutajio Jiburi LD Zenshuu (<b>Ghibli</b> Complete Collection: Studio <b>Ghibli</b> Complete LD Collection) from August 1996, the original March 1984 VHS version by Animage and re-release by Buena Vista on 19 September 1997. Three DVD sets were released in Japan with a regular DVD and figure set released on 19 November 2003 and a collectors set following on 7 December 2003.|$|E
